Press the button 3 times and hold on the third time till it starts blinking repeatedly
Immediately repeat process one until the switch blink slowly not as rapid as the first.
Release the button immediately you notice the slow blinking(if you don't, the process may fail).
After the button is released there's a blue light which shows it has been reset.
The LED goes off, wait till it comes back on and then hold the button down to set to pairing mode to readd# How to reset a lutron inline switch that has been added to a network before.
